### =============================================================
### AlAshmar API - Class Reports Controller
### Base URL: http://localhost:5107
### =============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5107
@authToken  = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@classId    = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000041
@semesterId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003

# =============================================================
# ClassReportsController  - Class-Level Reports
# =============================================================

### Get class daily report (today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class daily report (specific date)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/daily?date=2025-03-15
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class weekly report (current week)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/weekly
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class weekly report (specific week start)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/weekly?weekStart=2025-03-10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class monthly report (current month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class monthly report (specific month and year)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/monthly?month=3&year=2025
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class semester report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/semesters/{{semesterId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class attendance summary (all time)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class attendance summary (date range)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/attendance?fromDate=2025-01-01&toDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class points summary (all semesters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/points
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class points summary (specific semester)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/points?semesterId={{semesterId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class memorization summary (all semesters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/memorization
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get class memorization summary (specific semester)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/memorization?semesterId={{semesterId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###
